    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/hint.css/2.4.1/hint.min.css"><hr><blockquote><p>收集一些开发设备控制软件过程中发现的好用的包以及一些简单的用法，涉及到绘图、通讯、文件读写等操作。以及也会分享一些写程序和制作控件的心得。</p></blockquote><span id="more"></span><h1 id="绘图相关"><a href="#绘图相关" class="headerlink" title="绘图相关"></a>绘图相关</h1><h2 id="TeeChart"><a href="#TeeChart" class="headerlink" title="TeeChart"></a>TeeChart</h2><blockquote><p>待完成</p></blockquote><h1 id="文件读写相关"><a href="#文件读写相关" class="headerlink" title="文件读写相关"></a>文件读写相关</h1><h2 id="SharpConfig——CGF-x2F-INI设置文件的简单读写"><a href="#SharpConfig——CGF-x2F-INI设置文件的简单读写" class="headerlink" title="SharpConfig——CGF/INI设置文件的简单读写"></a>SharpConfig——CGF/INI设置文件的简单读写</h2><p><a href="https://www.nuget.org/packages/sharpconfig">nuget地址：<img src="https://buildstats.info/nuget/sharpconfig" alt="NuGet version"></a></p><p>在我的项目中主要用来进行项目设置、样品参数、加载程序段等数据的读写。原本使用 <code>.ini</code>文件存储文件信息，然后进行读写，操作较为繁杂，很难实现批量参数的快速读取和保存，代码写起来也不够简洁。</p><h3 id="cfg和-ini文件格式定义"><a href="#cfg和-ini文件格式定义" class="headerlink" title=".cfg和 .ini文件格式定义"></a><code>.cfg</code>和 <code>.ini</code>文件格式定义</h3><figure class="highlight ini"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 表示注释</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">[General]</span> <span class="comment"># 表示一节section</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">Somestr</span> = hello world! <span class="comment"># 表示一个键key及其值value</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">Somebool</span> = <span class="literal">true</span> <span class="comment"># 可以定义bool，int，double等变量</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">SomeArray</span> = {<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>} <span class="comment"># 定义数组</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">[Samples_a]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 第二个节，本项目中可以用来表示项目，或者每个样品单元的参数</span></span><br><span class="line">...</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h3 id="C-中的简单使用"><a href="#C-中的简单使用" class="headerlink" title="C#中的简单使用"></a>C#中的简单使用</h3><figure class="highlight csharp"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> SharpConfig</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// ----</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">xxxxx</span>{</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> config = Configuration.LoadFromFile(<span class="string">"sample.cfg"</span>); <span class="comment">// 加载cfg文件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> Gen_section = config[<span class="string">"General"</span>]; <span class="meta"># 加载其中节</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">String astr = Gen_section[<span class="string">"Somestr"</span>].StringValue; <span class="comment">// 读取key“Somestr”的值 </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">int</span>[] aintarray = Gen_section[<span class="string">"SomeArray"</span>].IntValueArray; <span class="comment">//</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 用户自定义类型 Sample</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> SampleA = config[<span class="string">"Sample_a"</span>].ToObject&lt;Sample&gt;();</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 新建一个configuration</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> myConfig = <span class="keyword">new</span> Configuration();</span><br><span class="line">myConfig[<span class="string">"Video"</span>][<span class="string">"Width"</span>].IntValue = <span class="number">1920</span>;</span><br><span class="line">myConfig[<span class="string">"Video"</span>][<span class="string">"Height"</span>].IntValue = <span class="number">1080</span>;</span><br><span class="line">myConfig[<span class="string">"Video"</span>][<span class="string">"Formats"</span>].StringValueArray = <span class="keyword">new</span>[] { <span class="string">"RGB32"</span>, <span class="string">"RGBA32"</span> };</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 保存“myConfig”</span></span><br><span class="line">myConfig.SaveToFile(<span class="string">"myConfig.cfg"</span>);   </span><br><span class="line">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h2 id="读写ini的方法"><a href="#读写ini的方法" class="headerlink" title="读写ini的方法"></a>读写ini的方法</h2><blockquote><p>待完成</p></blockquote><h1 id="用户自定义窗口与控件"><a href="#用户自定义窗口与控件" class="headerlink" title="用户自定义窗口与控件"></a>用户自定义窗口与控件</h1><h2 id="IP输入框"><a href="#IP输入框" class="headerlink" title="IP输入框"></a>IP输入框</h2><h1 id="施耐德PLC通讯协议"><a href="#施耐德PLC通讯协议" class="headerlink" title="施耐德PLC通讯协议"></a>施耐德PLC通讯协议</h1><script type="text&#x2F;javascript" src="https://unpkg.com/kity@2.0.4/dist/kity.min.js"></script><script type="text&#x2F;javascript" src="https://unpkg.com/kityminder-core@1.4.50/dist/kityminder.core.min.js"></script><script defer="true" type="text&#x2F;javascript" src="https://unpkg.com/hexo-simple-mindmap@0.8.0/dist/mindmap.min.js"></script><link rel="stylesheet" type="text&#x2F;css" href="https://unpkg.com/hexo-simple-mindmap@0.8.0/dist/mindmap.min.css">]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;收集一些开发设备控制软件过程中发现的好用的包以及一些简单的用法，涉及到绘图、通讯、文件读写等操作。以及也会分享一些写程序和制作控件的心得。&lt;/p&gt;
